                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>For an account of a visit in early 1954 of United States Representative to the
                    United Nations Trusteeship Council <persName corresp="#p_SM2">Mason
                        Sears</persName> to West <pb facs="0169" n="123" xml:id="pg_123"/> Africa
                    including the Belgian Congo, French Equatorial Africa, French and British
                    Cameroons, Nigeria, French and British Togoland, and the Gold Coast, see
                        <persName corresp="#p_SM2">Sears</persName>’ memorandum of June 3, 1954 to
                    Assistant Secretary of State for United Nations Affairs <persName
                        corresp="#p_KDM1">David Key</persName>, <ref target="frus1952-54v03#pg_1383"
                        >volume III, page 1383</ref>.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
